      "rdfs:comment": [
        "DEFINITION: A collection of terms approved and managed by some organization or person.",
        "NOTE: A controlled vocabulary is similar to a skos:ConceptScheme, but it could also be used for things that are not concepts, such as organizations, US presidents, geographic regions, etc. Hierarchical relationships between instances of the controlled vocabulary are possible."
      ],
